graph <- graph_from_data_frame(
    d = filter(e_dmp_lifecycle, (lifecycle == "FAIR" | lifecycle == "TRUST") ),
    vertices = filter(n_all, (source == "FAIR" | source == "TRUST" | source == "GEO") ),
    directed = FALSE)
